t-size="12" fill="#2563EB" text-anchor="middle" font-weight="700">Shortage = excess demand (Q₁ − Q₂)</text></g></svg>"`;

exports[`chart SVG regression > dynamic-efficiency.js renders unchanged SVG markup > ECONOS_DYNAMIC_EFFICIENCY_SPEC 1`] = `"<svg class="dynamic-efficiency-svg" viewBox="0 -16 460 336" xmlns="http://www.w3.org/2000/svg" font-family="Inter, sans-serif" role="img" aria-labelledby="econos-chart-title econos-chart-desc"><title id="econos-chart-title">Chart with AC₁ (today) curves</title><desc id="econos-chart-desc">Output (Q) on x-axis, Average cost (£) on y-axis. Curves: AC₁ (today).</desc><defs><clipPath id="econos-chart-clip"><rect x="58" y="20" width="384" height="264"/></clipPath><style>.de-1{opacity:0;visibility:hidden;transition:opacity .35s ease-out,visibility 0s linear .35s}.de-2{opacity:0;visibility:hidden;transition:opacity .35s ease-out,visibility 0s linear .35s}.sv-show-1 .de-1{opacity:1;visibility:visible;transition:opacity .35s ease-out}.sv-show-2 .de-1,.sv-show-2 .de-2{opacity:1;visibility:visible;transition:opacity .35s ease-out}.de-old-solid{opacity:1;visibility:visible;transition:opacity .35s ease-out}.sv-show-1 .de-old-solid,.sv-show-2 .de-old-solid{opacity:0;visibility:hidden;transition:opacity .35s ease-out,visibility 0s linear .35s}</style><marker id="econos-arrow-blue" viewBox="0 0 10 10" refX="9" refY="5" markerWidth="7" markerHeight="7" orient="auto"><path d="M 0 0 L 10 5 L 0 10 z" fill="#2563EB"/></marker><marker id="econos-arrow-amber" viewBox="0 0 10 10" refX="9" refY="5" markerWidth="7" markerHeight="7" orient="auto"><path d="M 0 0 L 10 5 L 0 10 z" fill="#D97706"/></marker><marker id="econos-arrow-green" viewBox="0 0 10 10" refX="9" refY="5" markerWidth="7" markerHeight="7" orient="auto"><path d="M 0 0 L 10 5 L 0 10 z" fill="#059669"/></marker><marker id="econos-arrow-red" viewBox="0 0 10 10" refX="9" refY="5" markerWidth="7" markerHeight="7" orient="auto"><path d="M 0 0 L 10 5 L 0 10 z" fill="#DC2626"/></marker><marker id="econos-arrow-slate" viewBox="0 0 10 10" refX="9" refY="5" markerWidth="7" markerHeight="7" orient="auto"><path d="M 0 0